      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NIGHT LIGHTER (1) is in hot form after clocking a powerful 16.88 victory two back then followed up with a 17.28 win at this track over 300m last time. Flying lately and looks hard to top. RED HOT BERNIE (8) finished in the minors last start over the 300m at this track but ran a sharp 17.13 last start. Has the ability and can measure up. FANCY THAT FRED (6) goes very well this course and distance starting 14 times for eight wins and two minors. Comes off a (16.92) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a Free For All over 300m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. CAPPADORA (2) placed last time out so worth considering.",
